Automation Test Strategy

Using python language, selenium and pytest libraries, 
I created an automation project following the Page Object Model design pattern
Test cases were created based on the gherking features using Test Driven Development.
The test cases chosen by me as the most critical were those that required the user to have manager permissions.
If I had to create a full automation test strategy I would choose to have
most automated test cases run api calls ( python requests library) and some end to end test cases using selenium.


Gherkin Test Cases : https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1LHcky-eOr9HKGdSe0O9W2a3YxDEHBQdPVXTjT0sUs28/edit?usp=sharing
